  "description": "Maximum cephalopod expression — the full alien display. chromaDepth holds at 0.6, colours already shifting across the skin. Mod wheel drives chromaDepth to 0.95 and armSpread to 0.88 simultaneously — a bilateral escalation into total display, the chromatophores firing at full bandwidth, arms flung wide, the signal overwhelming. Aftertouch triggers the ink cloud — a dense pulse of armour that darkens the texture suddenly before dissipating. Velocity controls armDepth: the quietest notes are still, precise, individual arm movements; hard strikes activate the full 8-arm gesture. The octopus at maximum declaration.",
